      <title>保时捷寻求在生产中断期间节省成本以保护利润率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/porsche-s-new-models-help-margins-after-tough-start-to-the-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于供应链障碍将影响多款车型的生产，保时捷汽车公司正计划采取新的成本削减措施来稳定利润率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/porsche-s-new-models-help-margins-after-tough-start-to-the-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉和 LVMH 业绩令人失望，股市暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司、路易威登集团和德意志银行公布的业绩不佳导致股市暴跌，在财报季即将到来之际，人们开始担心全球商业状况。纳斯达克 100 指数期货下跌逾 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国高等级债券销售创六年来七月份最高纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/us-high-grade-bond-sales-post-biggest-july-in-six-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蓝筹公司本月以六年来 7 月份最快的速度出售债券，以满足希望在美联储开始降息之前锁定高收益的投资者的强劲需求。]]></description>
